{"tid":639126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 長沙灣地盤鑽地機傾側　工人墮地昏迷","createTime":"2018-04-23T09:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T09:19:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab77fc1d14d794fe1d0feb743fff6e5a4c53b9e","tid":639126,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:01:32.000Z","msg":"長沙灣一地盤發生工業意外！上午8時許，長沙灣深旺道近東京街西，一個屬房屋委員會的建屋地盤，一部鑽地機疑失平衡突然傾倒，撞塌臨時工作台。一名36歲姓蘇工人由5米高墮地重傷，他右腳一度被工作台組件壓着。消防及救護員接報到場，救出事主，其右腳嚴重受傷，昏迷送院搶救。事件中，另有一名46歲姓李的工人走避不及，他腰部受傷，自行到醫院求醫。警方初步調查後，相信事件無可疑，事件列作工業意外有人意外受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/180974/%E9%95%B7%E6%B2%99%E7%81%A3%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E9%91%BD%E5%9C%B0%E6%A9%9F%E5%82%BE%E5%81%B4-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A2%AE%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F180974%2F%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E9%2591%25BD%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2582%25BE%25E5%2581%25B4-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlR5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=4d4d3291\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/180974/%E9%95%B7%E6%B2%99%E7%81%A3%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E9%91%BD%E5%9C%B0%E6%A9%9F%E5%82%BE%E5%81%B4-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A2%AE%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7</a>"},{"pid":"c998d0ec6c5f1c86c0515c2ffc14c3a52ada45e9","tid":639126,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303998e3dfd447092b2168b277c1b87b4ded365e","tid":639126,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:17:56.000Z","ms